ACKNOWLEDGMENTS

This software combines architectural patterns and features inspired by:

1. Gazelle (https://github.com/WhatCD/Gazelle)
   - Permission hierarchy system
   - Caching strategies
   - Tag voting system
   - Privacy controls (paranoia system)

2. Ocelot (https://github.com/WhatCD/Ocelot)
   - High-performance tracker patterns
   - Database write batching
   - Peer selection algorithms
   - Lock-free design patterns

3. Unit3d Community Edition (https://github.com/HDInnovations/UNIT3D-Community-Edition)
   - Bonus system architecture
   - Moderation workflow
   - Modern PHP/Laravel patterns
   - Media integration approach

These projects are acknowledged as inspirations for architectural decisions and
feature design. This implementation is an independent work built from scratch
in Rust with modern technologies.
